<br />
Although I'm not sure if that one will still require you to set a special price per item instead of at the category level. So you might have to look around a bit in the OpenCart extension directory for one that seems to meet your needs just right.<br />
<br />
Please let us know if you had any other questions at all!<br />
<br />
- Jacob</div>
